<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Titan" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Titan,</orth> the god of the sun: <bibl n="shak. ven 177" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 177</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.133" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 133</bibl> (in v. 134 it ought perhaps to be: <emph>pitiful-hearted butter</emph>). <bibl n="shak. tro 5.10.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 10, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.226" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 226</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.4.31" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 3, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.4.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 4, 166</bibl>.
